Soft stretch fabric moves with you, so feel free to lunge, leap, reach, lounge—make your move and these favorite boxer briefs are right there with you. A soft, non-constricting waistband with PUMA logo creates that perfect intersection of style and comfort. Flatlock seams offer a high-performance wear without chafing. Available in sizes: S, M, L, XL. PERFORMANCE MATERIAL: With 90% polyester and 10% spandex, you know you've got easy wear that's engineered to repel water and stay dry. And, wait, one more easy: our care instructions. Machine wash warm, do not bleach, tumble low dry at a low temperature, and wash with similar colors. Don't bother with dry cleaning or ironing. These boxer briefs are designed to make life easy. GO FOR THE PACK: The essential 5-Pack Active Stretch Boxer Brief from PUMA is an excellent choice for high-performance activity and all-day comfort.
